text: Cherry Creek is a census-designated place (CDP) in Arapahoe County, Colorado, United States. For the tributary of the South Platte River, see Cherry Creek (Colorado). The population as of the 2010 Census was 11,120.Colorado Trend Report 2: State and Complete Places (Sub-state 2010 Census Data). Missouri Census Data Center.
